 497          if cur > 0x7f : 
 498              cur = ord( buff.read(1) ) 
 499              result |= (cur & 0x7f) << 14 
 500              if cur > 0x7f : 
 501                  cur = ord( buff.read(1) ) 
 502                  result |= (cur & 0x7f) << 21

 507      return result

 509 -def readsleb128(buff) :
